Class SolarSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • sim.SolarSystem

  • public class SolarSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    russell, AJ The solar system contains the sun and whatever planets the user wants. It also stores information about the simulation, like time elapsed.
